---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Sponsors from "../components/Sponsors.astro";

const title = "Contacto - Baby Fútbol Funes 2025";
const description = "Contacta con los organizadores del torneo Baby Fútbol Funes 2025, clasificatorio al zonal nacional.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="bg-primary-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center">Contacto</h1>
      <div class="mt-2 h-1 w-20 bg-white mx-auto"></div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        ¿Tienes preguntas sobre el torneo? ¡Contáctanos!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Envíanos un mensaje</h2>
          
          <form class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Nombre completo</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="block w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-opacity-50" required />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Correo electrónico</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="block w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-opacity-50" required />
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label for="subject" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Asunto</label>
              <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" class="block w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-opacity-50" required />
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Mensaje</label>
              <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" class="block w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-opacity-50" required></textarea>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <button type="submit" class="w-full md:w-auto px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300">
                Enviar mensaje
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Información de contacto</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-100 text-primary-600">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Correo electrónico</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">info@babyfutbolfunes.co</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-100 text-primary-600">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Teléfono</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">+57 300 123 4567</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-100 text-primary-600">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Dirección</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
                  Oficina de Deportes Municipal<br>
                  Calle Principal #123<br>
                  Funes, Nariño, Colombia
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <iframe 
                src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d31875.31481422679!2d-77.49290195!3d1.0113954!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x8e2ed1fea7ef57a9%3A0x5cfdccd04deb3eb8!2sFunes%2C%20Nari%C3%B1o!5e0!3m2!1ses!2sco!4v1712003456123!5m2!1ses!2sco" 
                width="100%" 
                height="300" 
                style="border:0;" 
                allowfullscreen="" 
                loading="lazy" 
                referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              ></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Agradecimientos</h2>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          El torneo Zonal Regional BABY FÚTBOL FUNES 2025 es posible gracias al apoyo de las siguientes instituciones:
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x100?text=Alcaldía+de+Funes" alt="Logo Alcaldía de Funes" class="max-h-full" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Alcaldía de Funes</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Bajo el liderazgo del alcalde Jamez Cundar Zambrano, quien ha destinado recursos para garantizar un evento de alta calidad.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x100?text=Los+Paisitas" alt="Logo Los Paisitas" class="max-h-full" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Los Paisitas</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Organización que avala el torneo, garantizando que cumpla con los más altos estándares deportivos y formativos.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x100?text=Fundación+Fénix" alt="Logo Fundación Fénix" class="max-h-full" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fundación Fénix</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Entidad colaboradora en la organización del torneo, con el objetivo de promover el deporte en la región.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Sponsors />
</Layout>